Lyney' Demo Custom Weps List.

At the time of writing this, these weapons were seen in..
• Coldtown - 6 Scottish Pentathlon (Easy Adv)

The goal of this list is to be as honest and objective as possible.

Notes:
This mission were generally mediocre and borderline underwhelming
to the point where I never really bothered to test for any refund bugs that may not be mentioned here.

Custom Weapon

//===============
Primary
//===============

// NOT SEEN on RELEASE
  • Scatterbomb Shotgun (Coldtown) 
--Pretty strong. This seems untested for what its trying to do. Demo does CRIT Headshots?
--For the record, this is the TF2C equivalent of "just slap no random crits on it, its balanced now." - SiF
    // In-game Desc:
    // "Shotgun do bullet type, can Headshot" - Ian
      +150% Damage Bonus
      +Crits on headshot
      +100% max primary ammo
      (HIDDEN, COMMENTED OUT) Bullets explodes on impact
      (HIDDEN, COMMENTED OUT) -95.5% reduced self damage
      (HIDDEN) Attacks gain bullet as damage type

      No random crits
      (HIDDEN, COMMENTED OUT) -50% less accurate

// NOT SEEN on RELEASE
  • Fire ball Cannon (Coldtown) 
--Would not recommend. If it doesn't crash your game, its incredibly broken. +100 DMG and Burn.
    // In-game Desc:
    // "Fire the Fireball instead Grenade, -15% damage" - Lyney
      +Fires 100 Damage Fireball

      -15% Damage Penalty
      No random crits -- Fireball cannot do random crit, only minicrit.
      (HIDDEN) -50% Slower Firing Speed

// NOT SEEN on RELEASE
  • Nuke Cannon (Coldtown) // "FN | Hazard Warning Grenade Launcher" 
--Yikes. Nukesalot's mimic weapon. No comment. Read the stats.
    // In-game Desc:
    // "Deal 10x damage, Can't be upgrade" - Lyney
      +90% Damage Bonus
      +100% Grenade Explosion Radius
      +40% Faster holster and deploy
      No Reload Needed
      (HIDDEN) +300% Projectile Hitbox Size
      (HIDDEN) This weapon emits ("fluidSmokeExpl_ring_mvm") particles when explodes

      -125% Slower Reload Time
      -125% Slower Firing Speed
      -50% increased self damage
      -0.0375% max primary ammo
      No random crits
      (HIDDEN) Weapon cannot be upgraded -- None of the upgrades are purchasable.

  • Bouncing Betty (Coldtown) 
-- Ian Hunter's stats, still as busted. Max DMG = 252-756
    // In-game Desc:
    // "..." - Ian / Lyney
      +40% Damage Bonus
      -40% reduced self damage
      +100% Projectile Speed
      Grenades have very little bounce and roll
      Grenades explode on impact

      -25% Clip Size
      -50% Slower Firing Speed
      -30% Grenade Explosion Radius
      -38% Max Primary Ammo
      (HIDDEN) -40% self damage force
      (HIDDEN) No ammo from dispensers when active
  
