      -20% Stickybomb Explosion Radius

• Milky Stickybomb (Coldtown) // "FN | Gingerbread Winner Stickybomb Launcher" 
--Utterly worthless. 5 DMG on full upgr. Not full throwing, but still worthless.
      On Hit: 10s Mad Milked
      +35% Faster holster and deploy
      -0.5 sec faster bomb arm time
      -70% Max charge time
      -30% reduced self damage

      -90% Damage Penalty
      -50% Clip Size
      (HIDDEN) Weapon cannot be upgraded -- DMG, Heal on Kill are too expensive to buy.

• Regen Pack (Coldtown) 
--On Demo, the Cozy Camper is kind of okay-ish. Maybe you will throw a bit less hard, now.
    // In-game Desc:
    // "+20% move speed, +3 health regen and +25% bullet resistance. -30% healing from pack, healer and dispenser" - Lyney
      +3 health regenerated per second
      +25% bullet damage resistance
      +20% Faster Move Speed

      -70% health from packs
      -70% health from healer and medics
      (HIDDEN) Weapon cannot be upgraded -- Base weapon is gunboat, cannot purchase anything.

